ls -l

Example

-rwxr-xr-x
🛠 Task 2 – Change Permissions

Read only

chmod 444 file.txt

Executable

chmod +x script.sh

Owner only

chmod 700 script.sh
🛠 Task 3 – Change Ownership
sudo chown sachin:sachin file.txt

Directory

sudo chown -R sachin:sachin project/
🛠 Task 4 – Access Control Lists (ACL)

Install

sudo apt install acl

Grant permission

setfacl -m u:developer:rwx project/

View ACL

getfacl project/

Remove ACL

setfacl -x u:developer project/
