🛠 Task 8 – Firewall (UFW)

Status

sudo ufw status

Enable

sudo ufw enable

Allow SSH

sudo ufw allow 22

Allow HTTP

sudo ufw allow 80

Allow HTTPS

sudo ufw allow 443

Delete Rule

sudo ufw delete allow 80
🛠 Task 9 – iptables Basics

List Rules

sudo iptables -L

Allow SSH

sudo iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 22 -j ACCEPT
🛠 Task 10 – Password Policy

Install

sudo apt install libpam-pwquality

Edit

sudo nano /etc/security/pwquality.conf

Example

minlen=12

minclass=3

retry=3
🛠 Task 11 – SSH Hardening

Edit

sudo nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config

Recommended

PermitRootLogin no

PasswordAuthentication no

MaxAuthTries 3

X11Forwarding no

PubkeyAuthentication yes

Restart

sudo systemctl restart ssh
🛠 Task 12 – Fail2Ban

Install

sudo apt install fail2ban

Status

sudo systemctl status fail2ban

Check jails

sudo fail2ban-client status
